.org/web/20191207142745/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/plastic-memories/sub.blu-ray-1/.104833 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、《[[鬥陣特攻|鬥陣特攻]]》的[[D.Va|D.Va]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Allegra Frank |title=Heroes of the Storm skins reveal a love for classic anime |url=https://www.polygon.com/2017/5/10/15610360/heroes-of-the-storm-overwatch-dva-skins-evangelion |website=Polygon |language=en |date=2017-05-10 |access-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515084042/https://www.polygon.com/2017/5/10/15610360/heroes-of-the-storm-overwatch-dva-skins-evangelion |archive-date=2019-05-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在《{{link-en|格鬥天王 極限衝擊2|KOF: Maximum Impact 2}}》中，[[拳皇系列角色列表|蕾歐娜·海頓]]有一套類似明日香的戰鬥服裝，也有一套是類似綾波零所穿的服飾<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hg101.classicgaming.gamespy.com/kof/kof7.htm |title=Hardcore Gaming 101: King of Fighters |website= |access-date=2008-12-04 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218103433/http://hg101.classicgaming.gamespy.com/kof/kof7.htm |archive-date=2008-12-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。受影响的还有[[彩虹乐团|彩虹乐团]]的歌曲《あなた》，负责作曲的[[tetsu|tetsu]]看过电影《新世紀福音戰士劇場版》后，抱着希望明日香打开心扉的想法创作了该曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://anibu.jp/eva-character-song-17986.html|script-title=ja:実はけっこうある!?「エヴァ」キャラへ向けた歌！|date=2015-06-17|language=ja|access-date=2020-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802171543/http://anibu.jp/eva-character-song-17986.html|archive-date=2017-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

